# Cluedo Game - Jun Jin

## Project Description
This is a simplified command-line version of the classic Cluedo game developed in Python.  
The player can navigate between rooms and make suggestions to solve the mystery by guessing the correct combination of **Character**, **Weapon**, and **Room**.

## How to Run the Game

### 1Ô∏è: Clone the Repository
Use the following command to clone the project from GitHub:
https://github.com/JuneJin9655/Cluedo-Game.git


### 2: Navigate to the Source Code Directory
cd Cluedo-Game

### 3: Run the Game(Make sure you have Python 3 installed.)
python main.py
